name: There's no way back...
description:
What is There's no way back?

It's a platformer 2d game created by M4TT30 and Sorbet. This game was made for the Whisker game jam 2022 (https://itch.io/jam/whisker-jam-2022) in only 1 day with the theme "No way back"

What is the aim of the game?

You have to complete 3 basic platform levels, but you can only go forward. 

Commands

D  → - Movement 

Space - Jump

R  - Restart Level

Other information

For any feedback leave a comment down below or contact me on discord (M4TT30#4332)
